    <string name="about_text">This application gets movie information from a "Myfilms" API. Movies are classified as Top, Bottom, in theatres and Coming soon. Upon launching the app, the app displays the Movies screen with “intheaters”
movies. Tabs allow for other movies’ option selection.
When a user selects a movie, he is given options to watch the trailer (if signed in or prompted to sign in), to see full synopsis or view full movie  (of course this feature is not fully implemented, there are copy rights involved that the app developer needs to have for this to work.). </string>


